## Limitations
The analysis is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the potential for changes in economic policies that could alter the current trajectory of price increases. Additionally, the focus on tariffs and inflation may not capture all underlying factors contributing to rising prices, such as geopolitical events or unforeseen supply chain disruptions.